By: Theodore DeRego

Fission
=======

A simple 2D game engine based on SFML, Box2D, and ENet. It uses a component-entity based design, where you create
abstract game objects then add components to them.

Features:
 - Amazing 2D physics using Box2D
 - Easy animated sprite sheets.
 - Networking to make multiplayer games a breeze.
 - 2D lighting using LTBL, an add-on for SFML.
 - Easy weapons for all of your action games.
